00:21:38,800 --> 00:21:39,310
Kak San.

283
00:21:41,400 --> 00:21:42,070
Xiao Wu.

284
00:21:42,710 --> 00:21:43,230
Masuklah.

285
00:21:48,920 --> 00:21:49,430
