Dugu Bo.

324
00:24:05,040 --> 00:24:07,950
Terkena racun begitu lama,
pasti sudah ada keputusan.

325
00:24:08,640 --> 00:24:10,710
Kau sampaikan
permintaanku padanya.

326
00:24:11,520 --> 00:24:11,950
