00:24:23,530 --> 00:24:25,110
Aku temui
Master Dunia Racun sekarang.

331
00:24:27,560 --> 00:24:28,230
Tenang saja.

332
00:24:28,710 --> 00:24:31,040
Racunnya tak diobati,
