00:24:40,800 --> 00:24:41,280
Xiao Wu.

335
00:24:41,760 --> 00:24:43,280
Kau coba patahkan.

336
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:52,590
Hebat sekali.

337
00:24:52,800 --> 00:24:54,790
Apakah karena Cincin Roh
puluhan ribu tahun?

