384
00:28:00,190 --> 00:28:01,400
Aku akan pergi.

385
00:28:03,000 --> 00:28:03,590
Jika tak bisa?

386
00:28:04,520 --> 00:28:05,640
Aku akan membunuhmu.

387
00:28:07,040 --> 00:28:07,430
Baik.

388
00:28:08,070 --> 00:28:08,560
Mari.

389
00:28:23,350 --> 00:28:23,950
Nak.

390
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:27,470
Rumput Biru Perakmu memang kokoh.

391
00:28:31,950 --> 00:28:32,760
Teknik roh apa ini?

392
00:28:34,520 --> 00:28:37,560
Roh pelindung keluarga kami
tak ada teknik roh.

393
00:28:37,800 --> 00:28:38,800
Jadi, yang tadi itu apa?

394
00:28:39,560 --> 00:28:41,520
Kekuatan mencapai titik akhir.

395
00:28:42,400 --> 00:28:44,260
Mengeluarkan tenaga
dengan jentikan jari,…

396
00:28:44,680 --> 00:28:46,070
